original_title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อจุงง
overview: Prince Oak Oakleyski never attend the boxing ring but he established a street fight match on downtown avenue. He didn't seem to like indoor stadium because in this pandemic of Covid virus it is very easy to get infected if staying in indoor place without cool breeze. The open-air fighting avenue of Prince Oak Oakleyski has provided many premium seats made of tiger and lion fur. Every furniture was crafted by notable artisans. Textiles and pottery were the most beautiful inside arena of Prince Oak Oakleyski. Anyone can petition for a one-versus-one or dare to fight agin Prince Oak Oakleyski. But Prince Oak Oakleyski would eventually win because it's his supreme regulation. Not many people can rile the prince. However, the great fighter such as Oscar Dela Hoya is very handsome that he can team up with Prince Oak Oakleyski. Anyway, we love the prince of Eurasia so much. Lord Kandanai is controller of ukase and dictum. Prince Oak Oakleyski is supreme director of movies, undisputedly.
tagline: Prince Oak Oakleyski เจ้าชายโอค принц оьклейский
title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อจุงง
